Fabric - https://fabricmc.net


FoamFix - https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/foamfix-optimization-mod - FoamFix is a mod designed to optimize certain aspects of a modded Minecraft experience using simple, targeted optimizations
Clumps - https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/clumps - Clumps groups XP orbs together into a single entity to reduce lag when there are many in a small area

Sodium - https://modrinth.com/mod/sodium - Sodium is a free and open-source rendering optimization mod for Minecraft 1.16+ which greatly improves frame rates and stuttering while fixing many graphical issues
OR
OptiFabric - https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/optifabric - It allows Minecraft to run faster and look better with full support for HD textures and many configuration options

Starlight - https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/starlight - Mod for rewriting the light engine to fix lighting performance and lighting errors
*Lithium - https://modrinth.com/mod/lithium - Lithium is a modern, general-purpose optimization mod for Minecraft which works to improve a number of systems
FerriteCore - https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ferritecore-fabric - This mod reduces the memory usage of Minecraft in a few different ways
Distant Horizons - https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/distant-horizons - Simply put, it add simplified terrain past Minecraft's default view distance to improve performance and allow for longer draw distances

* = Not compatible with OptiFabric
